er management strategies may compromise bat conservation in rice paddies, requiring the adoption of alternative rice cultivation practices.", "access_right": "restricted", "creators": [{"name": "Toffoli, Roberto", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Rughetti, Marco", "affiliation": null}], "keywords": ["Biodiversity", "Mammalia", "Chiroptera", "Chordata", "Animalia", "bats", "bat"], "related_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/17e89b5427ba7132269bf601223a184b", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://sha256/c779a17478ed0aa9048aad8a43d84c5870720bc12c197f2633fa4712e2d636b0", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "zotero://select/groups/5435545/items/XK72XB24", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://zotero.org/groups/5435545/items/XK72XB24", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://linker.bio/cut:hash://md5/6e259bcf5c05bf97d3a09697ac814a01!/b165679-168163", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://md5/330417efcaa2560c9b8ebcd6fae17ce0", "relation": "isPartOf", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "10.5281/zenodo.1410543", "relation": "isCompiledBy", "resource_type": "software", "scheme": "doi"}], "custom": {"dwc:class": ["Mammalia"], "dwc:kingdom": ["Animalia"], "dwc:order": ["Chiroptera"], "dwc:phylum": ["Chordata"]}, "resource_type": {"title": "Journal article", "type": "publication", "subtype": "article"}, "journal": {"issue": "4", "pages": "687-695", "title": "Paddy and Water Environment", "volume": "18"}, "alternate_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/17e89b5427ba7132269bf601223a184b"}, {"identifier": "urn:lsid:zotero.org:groups:5435545:items:XK72XB24"}, {"identifier": "10.1007/s10333-020-00811-w"}], "communities": [{"id": "biosyslit"}, {"id": "batlit"}], "relations": {"version": [{"index": 0, "is_last": true, "parent": {"pid_type": "recid", "pid_value": "13483421"}}]}}, "title": "Effect of water management on bat activity i